    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, featuring a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts smoothly through all gears. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use on the driver's seat, and all electronic features are fully functional. While the exterior paint retains a nice gloss, there are a few small stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. It serves as a reliable, high-quality option for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
