      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with its care, keeping it garage-tucked and pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one! You\u2019ve really gotta see it in person to appreciate how stunning it is. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
