    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a peerless E46 M3, a definitive driver's machine preserved in concours-grade condition. At its heart lies the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has been meticulously sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known longitudinal stress points. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides precise gate selection, while the variable M differential lock ensures mechanical grip is maximized under load. Finished with original factory paint depth and a pristine underside, this vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and bushing integrity for an uncompromising, telepathic handling profile.",
      "price": 48500.0,
